    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815150/extras/0d2f1701d91b2f41622d7546b8683e21.avif?t=1753465825\" width=616 height=379 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ENTER THE WORLD OF RETAIL HORROR</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start your new job as a retail store employee  balancing stacking items on empty shelves, mopping up puke, maintaining the standards of the store, handling the constant requests of the rapid consumers and more...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A fast paced first-person anxiety-inducing thrill ride that invokes horror from the mundane of everyday life. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>I DON'T GET PAID ENOUGH FOR THIS!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the clock ticking down you'll have to resort to more extreme measures to ensure you finish your daily tasks and not upset The Manager. Hurl boxes at the consumers to temporarily stop them and run for your life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alternatively utilize the staff-only rooms which will act as temporary sanctuaries from the dreaded shop floor... but you can't stay there forever... </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fast-paced heart-pumping gameplay!  </strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple Nights </strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Extra Unlockables/Secrets</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PSX-style graphics</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815150/extras/cebd4b2fb3a32430e9343875b1247fdc.poster.avif?t=1753465825\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815150/extras/cebd4b2fb3a32430